---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="お問い合わせ" 
  description="柏原けやき苑へのお問い合わせはこちら。ご質問・ご相談などお気軽にお問い合わせください。"
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-keyaki-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-main">
      <p class="text-keyaki-300 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Contact</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-medium">お問い合わせ</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <div class="bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="container-main py-3">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-keyaki-700">ホーム</a></li>
          <li>/</li>
          <li class="text-gray-900">お問い合わせ</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact Info -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-main">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            ご質問・ご相談などがございましたら、お電話やメールフォームよりお受けしています。<br />
            施設見学も随時受け付けておりますので、お気軽にお問い合わせください。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <!-- Phone -->
          <div class="card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-keyaki-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-keyaki-700" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">お電話でのお問い合わせ</h2>
            <a href="tel:0795-73-1185" class="text-3xl font-bold text-keyaki-700 hover:text-keyaki-800 transition-colors">
              0795-73-1185
            </a>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">受付時間：8:30〜17:30（日曜・祝日を除く）</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Email -->
          <div class="card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-keyaki-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-keyaki-700" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/>
                <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">メールでのお問い合わせ</h2>
            <a href="mailto:keyaki-k@theia.ocn.ne.jp" class="text-xl font-bold text-keyaki-700 hover:text-keyaki-800 transition-colors break-all">
              keyaki-k@theia.ocn.ne.jp
            </a>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">24時間受付（返信は営業時間内）</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div class="card p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-medium text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">お問い合わせフォーム</h2>
          
          <form action="#" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                  お名前 <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  id="name" 
                  name="name" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keyaki-500 focus:border-keyaki-500 transition-colors"
                  placeholder="山田 太郎"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="kana" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                  フリガナ <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  id="kana" 
                  name="kana" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keyaki-500 focus:border-keyaki-500 transition-colors"
                  placeholder="ヤマダ タロウ"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                  メールアドレス <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="email" 
                  id="email" 
                  name="email" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keyaki-500 focus:border-keyaki-500 transition-colors"
                  placeholder="example@email.com"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="tel" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                  電話番号
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="tel" 
                  id="tel" 
                  name="tel"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keyaki-500 focus:border-keyaki-500 transition-colors"
                  placeholder="0795-00-0000"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="category" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                お問い合わせ種別 <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
              </label>
              <select 
                id="category" 
                name="category" 
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keyaki-500 focus:border-keyaki-500 transition-colors"
              >
                <option value="">選択してください</option>
                <option value="入所相談">入所に関するご相談</option>
                <option value="ショートステイ">ショートステイに関するご相談</option>
                <option value="デイサービス">デイサービスに関するご相談</option>
                <option value="見学">施設見学のお申し込み</option>
                <option value="採用">採用に関するお問い合わせ</option>
                <option value="その他">その他</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                お問い合わせ内容 <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
              </label>
              <textarea 
                id="message" 
                name="message" 
                rows="6" 
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keyaki-500 focus:border-keyaki-500 transition-colors resize-vertical"
                placeholder="お問い合わせ内容をご記入ください"
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <label class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <input 
                  type="checkbox" 
                  name="privacy" 
                  required
                  class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-keyaki-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-keyaki-500"
                />
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                  <a href="/privacy/" class="text-keyaki-700 hover:underline">プライバシーポリシー</a>に同意の上、送信してください。
                </span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <button type="submit" class="btn-primary px-12">
                送信する
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="m22 2-7 20-4-9-9-4Z"/>
                  <path d="M22 2 11 13"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Access -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-main">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="section-subtitle">Access</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">アクセス</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card overflow-hidden">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3269.8!2d135.05!3d35.1!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2zMzXCsDA2JzAwLjAiTiAxMzXCsDAzJzAwLjAiRQ!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1234567890"
            width="100%" 
            height="400" 
            style="border:0;" 
            allowfullscreen="" 
            loading="lazy" 
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            title="柏原けやき苑の地図"
            class="w-full"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-center text-gray-700">
          <p class="font-medium">〒669-3313 兵庫県丹波市柏原町北山289-1</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
